---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
	title="Privacy Policy - ResumeHub | Your Data Privacy Matters"
	description="Learn how ResumeHub protects your privacy. Our privacy policy explains data collection, usage, and protection in our free resume and CV builder."
	keywords="privacy policy,data privacy,personal information,resume data protection,CV privacy,data security,ResumeHub privacy"
>
	<div class="legal-page">
		<div class="wrapper">
			<header class="page-header">
				<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
				<p class="last-updated">Last updated: August 2025</p>
			</header>

			<main class="legal-content">
				<section>
					<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
					<p>ResumeHub is designed with privacy as a core principle. In our current development phase, we collect very limited information:</p>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>No User Registration:</strong> We do not require accounts or collect personal information through the website</li>
						<li><strong>Basic Analytics:</strong> Anonymous website usage statistics (page views, browser types) for platform improvement</li>
						<li><strong>Email Communications:</strong> Contact information only when you voluntarily email us for resume creation services</li>
						<li><strong>No Resume Data Collection:</strong> We do not store or process resume content through the website</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
					<p>The limited information we collect is used only to:</p>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>Website Analytics:</strong> Understand how visitors use our template gallery to improve the platform</li>
						<li><strong>Personal Service:</strong> Create custom resume websites when you contact us via email</li>
						<li><strong>Communication:</strong> Respond to your inquiries and provide support</li>
						<li><strong>Platform Development:</strong> Inform future feature development based on usage patterns</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
					<p>Since we collect minimal data, our security approach is straightforward:</p>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>No User Database:</strong> We do not maintain a database of user accounts or personal information</li>
						<li><strong>HTTPS Encryption:</strong> All website traffic is encrypted via HTTPS</li>
						<li><strong>Email Privacy:</strong> Resume content shared via email is handled confidentially and deleted after service completion</li>
						<li><strong>No Sale or Sharing:</strong> We never sell, rent, or share personal information with third parties</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
					<p>ResumeHub currently uses minimal third-party services:</p>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>Web Hosting:</strong> Static site hosting with no user data processing</li>
						<li><strong>Analytics (Optional):</strong> Anonymous usage statistics for platform improvement (no personal identification)</li>
						<li><strong>Email Service:</strong> Standard email for direct communications when you contact us</li>
					</ul>
					<p>All third-party services are chosen for their privacy-focused practices and minimal data collection.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>5. Your Rights and Control</h2>
					<p>Since we collect minimal data, your privacy rights are naturally protected:</p>
					<ul>
						<li><strong>No Account Data:</strong> No personal information is stored on our servers</li>
						<li><strong>Anonymous Browsing:</strong> Use the template gallery without providing any personal information</li>
						<li><strong>Email Control:</strong> Email communications are voluntary and can be discontinued at any time</li>
						<li><strong>Browser Settings:</strong> Disable cookies or analytics tracking through your browser settings</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>6. Children's Privacy</h2>
					<p>ResumeHub is intended for users 16 years and older. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 16. If you believe we have collected information from a child, please contact us immediately.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>7. International Users</h2>
					<p>ResumeHub serves users globally. If you are located outside the United States, please be aware that information you provide may be transferred to and processed in the United States.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>8. Future Features and Policy Updates</h2>
					<p>As ResumeHub evolves to include interactive editing features and user accounts (as outlined in our roadmap), this Privacy Policy will be updated accordingly. We will clearly communicate any changes to data collection practices and obtain appropriate consent before implementing new features that affect privacy.</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
					<p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at <a href="mailto:wendy7756@outlook.com">wendy7756@outlook.com</a>.</p>
				</section>
			</main>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

